WEBVTT

00:03.799 --> 00:04.468
Wonder.

00:05.367 --> 00:08.577
That feeling of surprise mixed with admiration,...

00:09.393 --> 00:11.133
...sparked by something beautiful,...

00:13.034 --> 00:14.437
...something unfamiliar,...

00:16.681 --> 00:19.299
...something you've been missing.

00:21.009 --> 00:22.356
It's that first look,...

00:25.201 --> 00:26.525
...that first taste,...

00:29.107 --> 00:30.598
...the new friends we make,...

00:33.129 --> 00:35.113
...and the loved ones we reconnect with,...

00:37.339 --> 00:38.949
...the stories that we tell...

00:41.322 --> 00:43.439
...and the memories we'll hold on to,...

00:45.488 --> 00:51.450
...a thousand miles away or just around the corner.

00:53.856 --> 00:56.059
Wonder is everywhere...

01:00.057 --> 01:01.739
...and we can help you find yours.

01:02.601 --> 01:05.022
Surrounded by lions on either side of the truck.

01:05.685 --> 01:06.517
It's emotional.

01:06.656 --> 01:08.035
It's working with your heart.

01:08.961 --> 01:11.219
The best works of art are all around me.

01:12.269 --> 01:13.835
Today is a miracle for me.

01:14.936 --> 01:17.201
Felt like we were hanging out with a group of friends.

01:18.264 --> 01:18.902
Viator.

01:20.343 --> 01:21.732
Find your wonder.

